snippet.textDisplay:
Beautiful production... I am loving all the international artists... Seriously, Amanda's voice, her vibe is lovely... Chirag sang in three languages and omg is actions make me watch the video over and over again... Magdi adds such a magical effect to the song, I mean arabic music has this special mesmerizing essence to it and Magdi did it so well... Quickstyle is awesome as always... And last but not the least, my heart screams for kaifi... His voice just hits so different... Magdi said it right that Kaifi's voice tells a hundred different stories... He does sound like many more years than he has actually lived... All of his songs, i listen to them on loop... They are all the best of the best.
The creative freedom that xulfi has given them all is what derives creativity... The way he has brought people from across the world together here in Pakistan... we cannot thank him rnough...and then the space he provided to all of them to practice their art... Excellence...It's like laissez faire which only works if all are passionate about their work... And when it works, it does wonders... Hats off to all the crew members, the set designers, the costume designer, the makeup artist, the musicians and everyone else... What a treat... Thanku Coke Studio... U make a Pakistan proud.
❤️✨❤️
